@id=1
@name=apple
@price=2
@type=fruit

### Create a new item
POST http://localhost:3001/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "{{name}}",
    "price": {{price}},
    "type": "{{type}}"
}

### Fetch an item
GET  http://localhost:3001/api/items/{{id}}

### Fetch a list of items
GET  http://localhost:3001/api/items


### Update an item
PATCH  http://localhost:3001/api/items/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "patch"
}